em Fokus auf der Schnittmenge von Informationstechnologie und architektonischer Formulierung entsteht so eine immer weiterführende intellektuelle Reflexion zu digitaler Architektur und Computerwissenschaft.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 4aArchitecture. 4aCode. 4aComputer Science. 7aARCHITECTURE / Study & Teaching.2bisacsh1 aBühlmann, Vera, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHovestadt, Ludger, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 a_ch3n81, Alice, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package English 2021z978311075072008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1z978311075070608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1z978311076682008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2021z9783110753783oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2021 Englishz978311075403208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPrinceton Architecture eBooks 2021z97831107565930 cprintz978303562401440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783035624052zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783035624052zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783035624052/original  a978-3-11-075070-6 DG Plus DeG Package